**DERP Knowledge Analysis & Verification Questionnaire**

Updated with Denver Revised Municipal Code (January 2024 Edition)
Verification

Date: February 21, 2026 \| Version: 2.0 \| Status: RMC-Verified

1\. Executive Summary

We have obtained and fully analyzed the Denver Revised Municipal Code
(DRMC), Sections 18-391 through 18-430.7, January 2024 edition, as
published by DERP. This 61-page document is the ultimate governing
authority for all DERP benefit provisions. Analysis of the complete RMC
text has allowed us to definitively resolve multiple critical and
high-priority items, significantly de-risking the POC build.

**Verification Status Summary**

