6.2 Demo Case Impact

**Case 1 (Robert Martinez):** No changes. Rule of 75 confirmed by
§18-402(20). All provisions verified.

**Case 2 (Jennifer Kim):** Early retirement rate already corrected to
3%. Now confirmed by statutory table in §18-409(b). \$1,633.07/month is
the verified amount.

**Case 3 (David Washington):** No changes. Tier 3 6% rate confirmed.
Rule of 85 confirmed by §18-402(20).

**Case 4 (Robert Martinez DRO):** Remove IPR for Patricia per
§18-418(b)(8). DRO division methodology confirmed. Verify COLA
applicability to former spouse\'s share (Q-DRO-03 remains open).

